Description

Please note that the product information displayed is provided by manufacturers, suppliers and other third parties and is not independently verified by Petco.

How about a fish tank that's tough as nails but looks like it's made of crystal? Our Aqueon Standard Open-Glass Glass Aquarium Tank can handle anything you throw at it (well, maybe not literally) and still look stunning. It's perfect for all kinds of aquatic creatures, so whether you're into goldfish or exotic tropical fish, this tank will provide a beautiful home for your finned friends.

  • - High-quality glass construction: This tank is built to last! You won't have to worry about cracks or leaks with our sturdy construction
  • - Clean silicone edges: We take pride in our attention to detail - the silicone edges are smooth and seamless, making for a sleek look
  • - For freshwater and marine applications: Whatever kind of fish you're into, this tank can handle it. Saltwater or freshwater, it's up to you!
  • - Not eligible for sale in Alaska and Hawaii: Sorry, guys - we wish we could ship everywhere, but these locations are off-limits for now
  • - Not eligible for price match: Trust us, though - this tank is worth every penny!
  • - 75-gallon size: Big enough to give your fish plenty of room to swim around and explore!

This product can expose you to Styrene, which is known to the State of California to cause cancer. For more information go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.

Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information for Targeted Advertising

To opt out of targeted advertising, cross-context behavioral advertising, and Selling/Sharing of your personal information, click the button so that it changes from blue to gray, and the button moves from right to left. When you are successfully opted out, the button will be gray and appear on the left side of the icon. Please note that after you opt out, you may still continue to receive generalized advertising that does not qualify as a sale or sharing under privacy laws.
